    <item>
      <title>由于关税需求前景，石油的价格接近六个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普总统的广泛关税在多个方面发动了贸易战争，因此在六个月内保持了最低水平的石油，这引起了人们对能源需求前景的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 23:29:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着日本收益率的增长，全球债券抛售越来越大：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四在亚洲加速了全球债券抛售，将日本的基准收益率提高到十多年来，在跨固定收益市场散布的德国款巨额销售后，将日本的基准收益率提高到了十多年。亚洲股票被延迟对墨西哥和加拿大的一些关税延迟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 22:36:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国银行国际银行削减商品部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/bank-of-china-international-makes-deep-cuts-to-commodities-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国银行国际控股有限公司是中国国有贷款人的投资银行业务部门，在过去几年中野国价转移使管理层对该行业的信心震惊之后，正在从商品中退缩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/bank-of-china-international-makes-deep-cuts-to-commodities-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 16:29:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
